Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その日は土曜日で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヴァイキングたちは土曜日に風呂に入る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:15.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼らのその習慣をイングランド人は知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てっ…敵襲だァァァーッ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,焼き尽くせ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,女子供とて容赦するな!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:41.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,皆殺しが王の御命令だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,持ちこたえろ！ ここが勝負どころだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,っしゃー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,スノーレ殺ったぞーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっそ～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よーし！ 槍部隊 前へーーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トツゲキーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あーあ  戦場があっち行っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:28.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もー  何でいつもすぐにやられちゃうんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死体はしゃべっちゃダメだ  トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:37.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おまえいっつも真っ先に死ぬよな ファクシ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん～～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:44.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天国にある“ヴァルハラ”では毎日お肉が食べられるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強い戦士じゃないと“ヴァルハラ”には入れないんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:52.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん～～ そっか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:58.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上や姉上は行けるのかな  ヴァルハラ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やられたか トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,雪の上で死ぬとカゼをひくぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,明日出発ぅ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いーなーいーなー！ 今度どこ行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルウェーさ  遊びじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,商売に行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:26.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,毛織物や毛皮を持ってって ワインなんかと交換するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃーボクも行く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:32.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だめ  じゃあってなんだ サラッと言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちェッ  ケーチ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,流水にぶつかっても知らないかんね！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,年末までにワインが欲しいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本国のみんなとイエス・キリストの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誕生日をワインで祝うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ボクの父上はミードが好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わけてもらえば？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワインを飲むことに意味があるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あるいはこの村にワインがあるかと思ったんだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:04.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一走り お前の父上に伝言を頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,軍船が来た
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんなもんでどうかな？ 親方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今度はふさがったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,水 入れてみな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,難しいもんだなァ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力を入れすぎなんだよ トールズさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちちうえーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここだ トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちちうえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また軍船が来たよ！ スゲーでっかいヤツ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:09.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,“戦鬼”のトールズを出せって言ったきり あのままだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズって… トールズさんだよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しかしありゃ半可な連中じゃねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:20.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハーフダンたちみてぇなゴロツキとは違うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ！ トールズさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴らこの村を攻める気じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヨームの戦士たちよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はここだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズさんに礼を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まさかここまで探しに来るとはな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,フローキ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:58.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルウェー遠征以来になりますな トールズ殿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よもやこのような最果ての地におかくれとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:07.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,用件を言え フローキ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では まずは上陸の許可を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何者なんだろうなァ  トールズさんって…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:19.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若い頃に戦働きをしてたとは聞いたけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,声がデケーよ アーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんまり自分のことを話さない人だからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おーい！ オレにも見せろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,“ヨームの戦士たち”って言ってたよな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前知ってるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁー…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんか父上 怒ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,入浴の最中を狙っての奇襲だったということです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:47.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デーンロー各地で多くのデンマーク人が イングランド軍に殺害されました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしてその中には
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デンマーク国王スヴェンの妹君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,グンヒルド様もいたとのこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,妹の仇討ち…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,スヴェン王はよい口実を得ました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大きな戦が始まります
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我ら戦士の出番です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いくさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:08.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,シッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヨーム戦士団はデンマーク軍と連合します
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来る春にはイングランドへの進攻が始まりましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,好きにするがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここは北の最果ての小村だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:26.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,北海の向こうで大国同士が何をしようと 関わりはない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうはまいりません
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:36.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が首領シグヴァルディの命令は“全艦隊ヨムスボルグに集結せよ”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,例外はない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おわかりかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その者がたとえ脱走兵といえどもね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,脱走…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヨーム戦士団大隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦鬼のトールズ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この度の戦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたも参戦するのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズ殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この度のことは我が首領の温情なのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,15年前行方不明になったあなたが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この度晴れて戦線に復帰する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:31.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すべてを不問にしてそういうことにしてくださるというのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:36.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が首領はそれほどに あなたの腕を惜しまれている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:42.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それを伝えるために 軍船で来ることはあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村の者が動揺している
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:50.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お変わりになられましたな あのトールズ殿が…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あるいはこの村が変えたのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:55.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,にげろーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やべやべっ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よい村だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供の様子でわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦災とは 今日まで無縁だったのでしょうな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞いたか？ 戦だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:16.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,スッゲェ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレ初めてだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わざわざ海越えてトールズさんを誘いにきたんだぜアイツら！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:25.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,スゲーよお前の親父さんは！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもよぉ… オレら連れてってもらえるかなぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オメェは無理だな 弱えェもん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んだよそれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱ強くねーとダメかぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁその点オレは大丈夫だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前ら人を斬ったことねーだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そーゆー経験があるかないかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ！ワリ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私もね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供の使いじゃないんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:02.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたがこたびの戦に加わらぬとおっしゃるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私は主命を果たせぬし 我が首領の面目も潰れる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:11.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうなれば とても手ぶらでは帰れません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おわかりでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヨーム戦士団
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヴェンドランドの港町 ヨムスボルグに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,基地を持つ軍団だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズが昔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヨームの戦士だったとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強いんすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強い
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あまりに強くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:45.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヴェンドランド王などは彼らから税金を取れないでいるほどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,北海最強を自負する軍団だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,撤収！ 全隊船に戻れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,撤収ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なに今の？ カンジ悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,助かったな アーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞かれよ村の衆！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はヨーム戦士団のフローキだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,主命により勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズ・スノーレソンに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,加勢を頼むためこの地へ参った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:25.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズ殿は！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:33.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が首領の求めに応じられ 軍船1隻の提供を約束なされた！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我と思わん者は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズ殿とともに ヨムスボルグへ参られよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ではトールズ殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いずれ戦場で会いましょうぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦だっっっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやいや何十年ぶりかのう  えっ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっしゃあ殺ったるでー！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦場に果てるは男の本懐よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうと決まれば明日っから船の準備だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,断れなかったのかね？ トールズ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村を巻き込んでしまったな…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人を殺すことで身を立てていた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもある日…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ある日 急に嫌になったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殺すのも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殺されるのも…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから逃げたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦場から…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:57.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死んだようにうまく見せかけたつもりだったんだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だったらもう一度…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃げればこの村がオレの代わりに報復される
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:10.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヨームの掟は脱走者を許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分のしてきたことに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けじめをつける時が来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おーし引くぞー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せェェェのォ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よいしょーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おら引けーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よいしょおーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ  レイフさん今日出港じゃなかったっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズに頼まれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その軍船と船団を組むことにしたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうかぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かにその方が安全だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イザって時はオレらが守ってやるからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よっと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃ頼もしい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,引け引けーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よいしょおーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しかしまぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どいつも戦好きなことよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,痛いよぉー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっそぉトルフィンのやつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,囲め囲め！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くぬヤロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やった！ やった！ トルフィン…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いってぇぇーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよ死ねよ トルフィン！ 今やられただろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ルール守れよな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだそうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだこいつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待てよトルフィン！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よーし！ 上げるぞーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いちにのっさんっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ようし！ もう一度いくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょっと診てやってくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イダーーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,折れてるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供の遊びにしちゃやりすぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひと月の間 添え木をしておいてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまんなトールズ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンがやったんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつ最近ムカつくんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手加減しねーし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もー絶対仲間に入れてやんねー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当か？ ウチの子が？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん…ウゥ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そ…それはすまなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よく言って聞かせる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気にすんなョ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供同士のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもまだ6つだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,4つ5つ上の子たちにケガさせるたぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たいしたもんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いい戦士になるぜあの子は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱりあんたの血だよ トールズ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ一式くれんの？ オヤジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:04.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ははっ じいさまの代からの家宝の武具だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,存分に戦ってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かっけーぞ アーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレのも見てくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,馬の首を一撃で落としたっつー名品だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おー！ デケェな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,エモノったら槍だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おー？ なんなら勝負すっか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もーあんたって子はぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでもかんでも放りっぱなしにすんなよな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ってコラ聞いてんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,片づけないと捨てちゃうよ！ いいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いい  もういらない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんなのよ物置ひっくり返して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウチの武器はどこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁ？ ブキ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ボクには武器が必要なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,武器があれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた さては
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:56.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦士になって父上の船に乗せてもらっちゃおーとか考えてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ゆっとくけどねー ムダな努力よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたみたいなチビッ子が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:54.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きれい…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なに？ どうしたのユルヴァ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,剣が欲しいか トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,剣は人を殺す道具だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:21.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前はこれで  誰を殺すつもりなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てっ… 敵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の敵は誰なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハーフダンとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よく聞け トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前に敵などいない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:54.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰にも敵などいないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,傷つけてよい者など どこにもいない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっ… おかしいよそんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だって父上は明日いくさに行くんでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵を殺しに行くんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こどもじゃない…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上はウソを言ってる…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ボクにだってわかる！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うわっ トルフィン？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,スキあり！ あぶねーって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:42.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヘルガ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:44.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの子を…頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,西北西から微風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,波 穏やか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:16.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今朝はオーディン神の機嫌がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出港にはいい朝だな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よぉーし言ったな！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:39.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,左手で投げて命中ならその酒ダルはオレのもんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おお… 主よ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いくぞ～キリスト坊主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よけたら殺すぞ～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:54.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てんめ！ よけたろ？ 今よけたろ？ 殺す！ マジ殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どけよ 次はオレだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ… 神父さま…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからよけんじゃねっつの！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:06.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おめぇがヘタなんだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オォイ！ ヨームの兄さん方！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたらも一杯やらねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お行儀がよくていらっしゃる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:19.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほっとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,安酒はお口に合わねんだとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:33.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,相変わらず貴様の手下は品がないな  アシェラッド
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:39.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,キリスト教が好かねぇだけですよ フローキのだんな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それより… さっさと仕事の話をしましょうや
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:49.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手下どももオレも こんな僻地で待たされて退屈してたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:52.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大きな変更はない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,報酬は金5ポンド
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:01.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴の死体と引き換えでなければ払わんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:06.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴の船と積み荷はお前たちの好きにしていい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:11.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズを殺せ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:22.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,To sink or swim 生き残るために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:25.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Dog eat dog world だと言い聞かせる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:27.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Surviving with the fate, it’s 弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:35.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Face a world that our wisdom only will tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,What went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:39.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,What went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:44.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,I’ve paid my dues, I’ve sold my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:48.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,So tell me what is left for me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,When I’ve given up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:53.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねえ　取り替えてたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:59.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どの景色を見ても　何も感じなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:03.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねえ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:11.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの景色を求めていた　僕は無感情だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねえ　取り替えてたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:20.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どの景色を見ても　何も感じなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:24.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねえ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:31.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの景色を求めていた　僕は無感情だろう{Source: https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/lyrics/survive-said-the-prophet/mukanjyo/}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:20.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,It’s just like a burning torch in the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:25.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Like a little flower blooming in the home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:31.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強く確かな意志を掲げ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:36.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ときに優しくあればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:41.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,I’m missing you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:49.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,I’m missing you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:54.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,滲む景色に膝を抱き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,胸をはせる時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:03.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, sail away again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:10.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,未開の海に回路を照らす願い
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.78,0:24:16.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,繋いだ声は　答えのない世界へと
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:20.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,帆を揺らす You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.73,0:24:24.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ荒波をゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:32.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その闇に向け{Source: https://www.lyrical-nonsense.com/lyrics/aimer/torches/}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:13.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,NORTHERN ENGLAND EARLDOM OF NORTHUMBRIA \NVIKINGS' BASE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Vikings bathe on Saturdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The English knew about this custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't spare the women or children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them all. Those are the king's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed Snorre.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Spear troops, advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The battlefield went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I always get killed so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead men aren't supposed to talk, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always the first one to die, Faxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In Valhalla, in heaven, \Nyou get to eat meat every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't enter Valhalla \Nunless you're a strong warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my mother and my sister \Nwill get into Valhalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they kill you, Thorfinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you die in the snow, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky. Where are you going this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To Norway. I'm not going there for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to trade goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I take wool and fur, and trade it for wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No. What do you mean, "then"? \NDon't say it so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're so stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you end up hitting an ice floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get some wine before the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to celebrate the birth of Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with the people of my home country \Nwith some wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My father likes mead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask him for some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there'd be some wine in this village, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you pass on a message to your father for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A warship has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The leak's been fixed this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Try putting some water in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You put too much strength into it, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Another warship came. It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked for Thors the Troll. \NThey've been waiting there ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors? Are they talking about Thors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Troll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not like Halfdan's thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they planning to invade this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jomsvikings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're bowing to Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined you'd come this far looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Floki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen each other \Nsince the Norway campaign, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined you'd be hiding here, \Nat the end of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your business, Floki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. First give us your permission to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Thors?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he used to work on the battlefield \Nwhen he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll hear you, Ari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't talk about himself much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Jomsvikings," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Know anything about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Father is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They made a surprise attack while they were bathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Many Danes were killed \Nby English troops in Danelaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunhilde,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the sister of Sweyn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the King of Denmark, was one of the victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge for his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sweyn has a good excuse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A big war is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for us warriors to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-War? \N-Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jomsvikings will join the army of Denmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our invasion of England will begin \Nthis coming spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a small village \Nat the northern edge of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever these big countries on the other side \Nof the North Sea decide, it's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That will not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader Sigvaldi ordered me \Nto gather the entire fleet at Jomsborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that man deserted the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Deserted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain of the Jomsvikings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors the Troll.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a war...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you too will fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader is doing this out of his own goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After going missing 15 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a chance \Nto return to the battlefield with honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader is willing to overlook everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how much our leader wants you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to come on a warship \Njust to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed a lot, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did this village change you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run away. \N-Run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a nice village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell from the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They've lived a life free from war, until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that? There's going to be a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wow. \N-This is my first war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He came all the way across the ocean to invite Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if he'd take us with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no chance. You're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you talking about? \N-You're no good unless you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I got that covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never killed anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on whether \Nyou've had that experience or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a powerless messenger, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're saying you're not going to fight in the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't carry out my master's orders, \Nand our leader's reputation would be damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back empty-handed in a situation like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jomsvikings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're an army with a base in Jomsborg,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a port town in Wendland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that Thors used to be a Jomsviking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that the King of Wendland was unable \Nto collect taxes from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They take pride in being the strongest army \Nin the Northern Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw. All troops, return to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that just now? That was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saved, Ari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Floki of the Jomsvikings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At the orders of my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to this land
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask the hero Thors Snorresson to join our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader has requested
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that Thors be provided with one warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have what it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,join Thors and come with us to Jomsborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall meet on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-How many decades has it been? \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be an honor to die on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started right away. \NLet's prepare the ships tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you couldn't say no, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I dragged the village into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to earn my living by killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I suddenly hated it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I ran away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I succeeded in making it look like I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You could do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I run away, this village will be punished in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jomsvikings never forgive deserters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to take responsibility \Nfor what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave, ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave, ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave, ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I thought you were leaving today, Leif.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to join the fleet with that warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll protect you in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull. Pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave, ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Though,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone really does love war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn you, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it. I killed Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you? Die, Thorfinn. \NYou got killed just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone hit too hard. \NIt's supposed to be a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the splint on for one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never playing with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true? My son did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to him about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take it so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's between the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only 6, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can hurt kids \Nthat are four or five years older than him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,he must be pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll grow up to be a good fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes after you, Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving me all of this, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're family treasures from my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight with all your might.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You look good, Ari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It can cut off a horse's head in one stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Spears are what's best for plundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Want to have a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw everything on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw it away \Nif you don't pick it up. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. I don't want it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, \Nsearching through the storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are our weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to become a warrior \Nand sail on your father's ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you now, \Ndon't waste your time trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A little kid like you can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's wrong, Ylva?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want a sword, Thorfinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A sword is a tool for killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were you planning to kill with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The... The enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is your enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Halfdan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has any enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one who it's okay to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you're going off to war tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to kill the enemy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-You let your guard down. \N-That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Helga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind blows faintly from the west north-west.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The waves are calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Odin is in good spirits this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good morning for your departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,FAROE ISLANDS \NSTREYMOY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I throw left-handed and hit it, \Nthe barrel is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way. \N-You can talk after you hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go, Christian monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you dodge, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard. You dodged. \NYou dodged just now. I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Move. It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. The priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jomsvikings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They have good manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they don't like cheap alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How many points do I get for his leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your men don't have any class, Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We just hate Christians, Floki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough about that. Let's get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My men and I are bored of being kept here waiting \Nin the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no major changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be compensated with five pounds of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will only pay you in exchange for his dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do whatever you want with their ship, \Nand their cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Thors.
